data.description: Beautiful 4 bedroom, 2 bath BRICK home located in the much desired subdivision of Heritage Park. Home features include spacious floor plan, decorative tile & wood floors, high ceilings, wood burning fireplace, upgraded lighting, formal dining with separate breakfast nook, stainless steel appliance package, new plantation shutters in living area, expansive master suite with garden jacuzzi tub, double vanities, walk in shower and custom closet shelving in the walk in closet. Home also boast another room off kitchen that could be a study/library or sitting room with endless possibilities for additional space and workshop shelving & sink built into garage and includes custom made hurricane shutters. Relax on the the recently glassed in porch with added air vent and french-doors with built in shades overlooking a private and large backyard stunning lake views! Amenities galore including; clubhouse, exercise room, pool, tennis, basketball and  pickleball courts, nature trails and walking paths, playgrounds and more. Located close to shopping, downtown St. Augustine, beaches and A+ rated schools. Most furnishings can be purchased separately
